==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Millenarian
<hw>Mil`le*na"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Millenary</er>.]</ety> <def>Consisting of a thousand years; of or
pertaining to the millennium, or to the Millenarians.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Millenarian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Millenarian
<hw>Mil`le*na"ri*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who believes that
Christ will personally reign on earth a thousand years; a
Chiliast.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Millenarism</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Millenarianism</ent>⟦br⟧
